title: My Blood Moon Yasuo from Gamekit
body: My Blood Moon {{champion:157}} went missing and i need help at it. Pls comment below if there's just a bug there.

replies.body: Unfortunately, I don't have any details that I'd be able to offer on your specific issue.  Reach out to us in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we can provide context and see what's up.  We'll reply as soon as possible!
